snippet.title: City Zoomer Game Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1745790/City_Zoomer/

City Zoomer is a fast-paced movement focused endless runner. Endless streets filled with unpredictable drivers are ahead. Zoom your way through the city at fast speeds to see how long you can last before making careless mistakes.
